titles.title: To suspend for 3 years the duty on methoxyfenozide.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

committee.name: House Committee on Ways and Means

bill.summary: 6/10/1999--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 2002, the duty on benzoic acid, 3- methoxy-2-methyl-,2-(3, 5-dimethylbenzoyl)-2-(1,1-dimethyl ethyl) hydrazide (methoxyfenozide).
